name: You Came Early
description:
You came early to the game and you are in the wrong place. What do you do?

You Came Early is a cute little shooter platformer.

There are multiple endings to the story

Keep in mind this game has been made by 1 person in 12 days and this is my first game jam

Game Engine: Game Maker Studio 2
